      Created by Shaman
      Access your new links:

      ğŸŒ Web server: http://localhost/
      âš™ï¸ PHPMyAdmin: http://localhost:8080
      âœ‰ï¸ Local emails: http://localhost:8025

===================== ğŸš€ Done ğŸš€ ==================="

bash install-m2
